Class CLibrary.T_dqblk

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.jna.Structure
      • it.grid.storm.api.filesystem.quota.posix.CLibrary.T_dqblk
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Enclosing interface:
    CLibrary

    public static class CLibrary.T_dqblk
extends com.sun.jna.Structure
implements com.sun.jna.Structure.ByReference
    T_dqblk is the correspondent of the dqblk structure defined in sys/quota.h and returned by reference as addr field after quotactl() call with Q_GETQUOTA.
    Author:
    Enrico Vianello
